                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with a previous conviction of felony at Clerkenwell in March</hi>, 1876, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
PLEADED GUILTY</hi>**—<hi rend="italic">
